title: Disney Classic Games Collection Remastered
description:
NEW! 16 New Games: A Bugs Life, Arcade Frenzy, Brave, Buzz Lightyear of Star Command, Castle of Illusion, Donald Duck Cold Shadow, Emperors New Groove, Goofy's Extreame Skateboarding, 
Lilo & Stitch Trouble In Paradise, Tangled, Timon and Pumbaa Burper, Peter Pan - Adventures In Neverland, Mickey Saves the day, Toy Story 3, WALL-E and Tarzan with all the sounds and cinematics from the original version. 
Some games now have improved compatibility with Windows 10 for others (*) I have included VirtualBox.

The launcher has new enchanted visuals, fullscreen slideshows with more screenshots, ultra hi-res posters

A classic collection of Disney games from 1990 to 2013. Simply mount, install and play. Burn, print and keep. 

Some setups might be in russian but the games are 100% english.
